Sure, here are some example sentences using the word "mozgu" in different forms and positions:

1. *Mozgu* je potrebno vreme da se oporavi od povrede. (The brain needs time to recover from an injury.)
2. Njegov *mozak* je bio pod velikim stresom. (*His brain* was under a lot of stress.)
3. Ovaj lek pomaže u poboljšanju *mozgovne* funkcije. (This medication helps improve *brain* function.)
4. Naučnici proučavaju *mozgovne* talase tokom spavanja. (Scientists study *brain* waves during sleep.)
5. *Mozgi* su mu bili iscrpljeni od preteranog rada. (*His brains* were exhausted from overworking.)
6. Želim da se fokusiram na svoj *mozak* i unutrašnji mir. (I want to focus on my *mind* and inner peace.)

Note: In Serbian, the word "mozak" refers to the physical organ of the brain, while "mozak" and "mozgi" can also refer to the mind or mental capabilities in a more abstract sense.